prompt_text: Describe the scene of a flood.
content_text: A flood is a terrifying scene. Sometimes men, an woman can be seen clinging to the trees or crying for help on the roofs of their houses during floods. During floods, the government have to take immediate relief san rescue measures and sanction huge funds for the purpose to alleviate those suffering of the victims of flood. Relief camps are open where people are provided with shelter, food, clothing, medicine, etc. People also do great generals. Generously to the flood Relief Fund.
